{"data":[{"date":"13:56 03/07","title":"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal c\u1eb7p k\u00e8 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a h\u00f4n v\u1edbi Chicharito","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hau-ve-carvajal-cap-ke-phong-vien-tung-hua-hon-voi-chicharito.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m gi\u1eefa tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 b\u00f2 t\u00f3t Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Lucia Villalon.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Chicharito xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f4 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal. Lucia Villalon mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb c\u00f9ng Carvajal c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pilar Rubio, Sara Salamo v\u00e0 Beatriz Espejel (n\u1eeda kia c\u1ee7a Sergio Ramos, Isco Alarcon v\u00e0 Koke) c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a h\u00f4n v\u1edbi Chicharito h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a h\u00f4n v\u1edbi Chicharito h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/cc2-1635-1530586577.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lucia Villalon v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecnh m\u1edbi Carvajal. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Lucia Villalo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico Javier Hernandez Chicharito. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Daniel Carvajal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid\", t\u1edd AS b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Nga 2018, Lucia Villalon l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i World Cup cho hai \u0111\u00e0i Univision v\u00e0 Televisa Deportes. Tuy v\u1eady, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sau khi tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3c l\u00f3c cho m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i gi\u1eadn d\u1eef, b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 sau k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t hay x\u1ea5u, v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n\", Lucia Villalon c\u00f2n tag th\u00eam d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef \"T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 anh\" c\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLucia Villalon v\u00e0 Carvajal t\u1eeb l\u00e2u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3957","checkdouble":"190272"},{"date":"14:09 03/07","title":"Nam ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean m\u1eb7c v\u00e1y \u0111i l\u00e0m sau khi Nga v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nam-phong-vien-mac-vay-di-lam-sau-khi-nga-vao-tu-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3956","checkdouble":"190273"},{"date":"14:36 03/07","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t fan cu\u1ed3ng Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/them-mot-fan-cuong-messi-tu-tu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t C\u0110V \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn thua 3-4 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn Argentina thua Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 t\u00ean Monotosh Halder, \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Malda (t\u00e2y Bengal), \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMonotosh Halder \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan cu\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Leo Messi. Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng Argentina v\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Leo Messi thua Ph\u00e1p qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup, Monotosh Halder \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 b\u1ecf \u0103n t\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111i ng\u1ee7 ngay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/NINTCHDBPICT000415355840-e1530544891798.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dinu Alex, C\u0110V \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn Argentina thua Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e1ng h\u00f4m sau, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 g\u1ecdi d\u1eady, Monotosh Halder \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng g\u00ec. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Monotosh Halder, cha m\u1eb9 C\u0110V \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eaft th\u1edf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCon t\u00f4i l\u00e0 C\u0110V Argentina. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb \u1ed1m. N\u00f3 d\u00e1n m\u1eaft v\u00e0o TV k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi World Cup kh\u1edfi tranh. Ch\u00e1u n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 qu\u1eabn tr\u00ed khi Argentina thua nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y\u201d, \u00f4ng Mongol Halder, cha \u0111\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Monotosh Halder cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Malda th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u tra v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Argentina\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Dinu Alex, 30 tu\u1ed5i, fan cu\u1ed3ng Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi bang Kerala (ph\u00eda nam \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9) c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y s\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3955","checkdouble":"190276"},{"date":"15:35 03/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 5-0 U19 Philippines (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-philippines-15h30-ngay-37.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 0-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu do d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U19 Philippines.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-299-190079.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-299-190079.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng BXH - LT\u0110 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLink xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp (Fanpage Onsport): <span href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Onsportchannel/videos/588930214837934/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.facebook.com/Onsportchannel/videos/588930214837934/</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- HLV\u00a0Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ebf 8 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, Thi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n Nam l\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/doi-hinh-xuat-phat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1eadm. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 12: Minh B\u00ecnh v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc b\u00f3ng \u0111i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 20: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m sao ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp trung b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 22: U19 Philippines \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi Ph\u1ea1m\u00a0V\u0103n Nam ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt may, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00ca\u0111\u00ea Y E Li Ni \u00ca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 26:\u00a0Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Minh B\u00ecnh t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa b\u00ean trong kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 30: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U19 Philippines.\u00a0R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a \u01b0u th\u1ebf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi L\u00ea V\u0103n Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB\u00a0H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay, v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 39: D\u00f9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n U19 Philippines v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c song ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 42:\u00a0QU\u00c1 \u0110\u00c1NG TI\u1ebeC. Minh B\u00ecnh c\u0103ng ngang qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t L\u00ea V\u0103n Nam v\u00e0o t\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly c\u00f3 v\u00e0i m\u00e9t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft th\u00fac ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0T\u1ea5n Ho\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 50: U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 2-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho L\u00ea V\u0103n Nam ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 55:\u00a0U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 3-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. S\u1ed1 18 Minh\u00a0B\u00ecnh, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o\u00a0HAGL, l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-0 v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 65: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 h\u00f2ng mang ra d\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh l\u00fac c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 73: U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 4-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 4 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 82: U19 Philippines su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat xa uy l\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 86:\u00a0U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 5-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. Trung v\u1ec7 Duy Ki\u00ean c\u1ee7a HAGL\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n sau qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i theo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV\u00a0Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n\u00a0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Philippines 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 37 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Philippines 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 37 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Truc-tiep-U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Philippines-15h30-chieu-hom-nay-37-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3954","checkdouble":"190270"},{"date":"15:08 03/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u00e0 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/21/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-chelsea-len-80-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Barca quan t\u00e2m Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Chelsea-ban-Willian-voi-gia-80-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u00e0 Barca quan t\u00e2m Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Mourinho c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. N\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willian r\u1eddi Chelsea l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Barca \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u euro song Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian\" title=\"Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/23/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-willian-cho-barca-nhung-mu-thi-khac.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t xu h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Willian ra \u0111i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n80 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady M.U v\u00e0 Barca d\u00f9 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i suy\u00a0ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3953","checkdouble":"190275"},{"date":"15:55 03/07","title":"Real Madrid ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Neymar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/17/neymar-phu-nhan-mua-neymar-voi-gia-ky-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00f4ng tin Real Madrid mua Neymar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 310 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh TVE c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Los Blancos th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Neymar</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin Real mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar t\u1eeb PSG. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 310 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y! th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Neymar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Neymar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/neymar-phu-nhan-mua-neymar-voi-gia-ky-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Neymar&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Neymar do \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh TVE c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u1edd b\u00e1o l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-gui-psg-200-trieu-euro-kroos-va-bale-neymar-180-186769.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Neymar</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNHM quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0i TVE c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t ph\u00eda Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Neymar</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin Real Madrid mua Neymar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 310 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh TVE c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Los Blancos th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar PSG vs Real Madrid\" title=\"Neymar PSG vs Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/15/neymar-va-psg-khi-chung-ta-khong-thuoc-ve-nhau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin mua Neymar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh TVE \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin Real mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Neymar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 310 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real h\u1ecfi mua Neymar, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o v\u1edbi PSG c\u1ea3&rdquo;.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Real Madrid ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh TVE c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3952","checkdouble":"190280"},{"date":"15:41 03/07","title":"Juventus s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i \"bom t\u1ea5n\" v\u1edbi Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/juventus-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-chelsea.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Gonzalo Higuain theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Gonzalo Higuain thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ch\u1ec9 ghi 16 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 Higuain, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 Higuain, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/16/San-sang-nha-Higuain,-Juventus-muon-mua-Alvaro-Morata-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf Stamford Bridge. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u1ec9 ghi 11 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n&nbsp;tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Morata l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Alvaro Morata t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Real Madrid. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Italia, Juventus tin r\u1eb1ng Morata s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Huguain l\u1ea5y Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/morata-chinh-thuc-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-172-189985.html\" target=\"_blank\">Morata n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 Higuain, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"S\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 Higuain, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/juventus-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-chelsea.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Gonzalo Higuain theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Higuain, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chung \u1edf Napoli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Higuain l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Morata qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eadn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n ra m\u1eaft Chelsea. Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3951","checkdouble":"190279"},{"date":"16:23 03/07","title":"Ajax ch\u1ec9 mua l\u1ea1i Daley Blind v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ajax mua Daley Blind c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Daley Blind</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaley Blind ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ajax trong 6 n\u0103m, t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2008 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2014. Sau \u0111\u00f3 anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2014 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ajax mua Daley Blind ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ajax mua Daley Blind ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Ajax-mua-Daley-Blind-chi-xay-ra-voi-mot-dieu-kien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Blind</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Blind r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, \u1edf Old Trafford anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, Blind kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Blind, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Blind v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-daley-blind-neu-roi-mu-172-190201.html\">Ajax l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Blind nh\u1ea5t</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan. Theo The Sun, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ajax ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Blind v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajax mua Daley Blind c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind\" title=\"Daley Blind\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax, Daley Blind bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Blind \u0111ang nh\u1eadn 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf M.U, ph\u00eda Ajax ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 60.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBlind s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf M.U. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3950","checkdouble":"190284"},{"date":"17:06 03/07","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Sevilla t\u1edbi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/sao-tuyen-phap-nang-nac-doi-roi-sevilla-toi-arsenal.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, cha c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 con trai m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Steven Nzonzi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Xhaka th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/17/Arsenal-mua-Steven-Nzonzi-cua-Sevilla-voi-gia-22-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Steven NZonzi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXhaka kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ec9 quanh qu\u1ea9n \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n v\u00e0 b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao. HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n h\u01a1n 40 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n v\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Steven Nzonzi, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Steven Nzonzi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, cha c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 con trai m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\" zonzi=\"\" muon=\"\" den=\"\" title=\"N\" mu\u1ed1n=\"\" \u0111\u1ebfn=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/sao-tuyen-phap-nang-nac-doi-roi-sevilla-toi-arsenal.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>N'Zonzi mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, sau 3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Sevilla, Nzonzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Nzonzi v\u1edbi Sevilla c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi ra 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-leicester-tranh-gianh-tien-ve-tru-cua-sevilla-172-135571.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Steven Nzonzi</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Kante. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Stamford Bridge khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 HLV Unai Emery t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Steven Nzonzi \u1edf Sevilla, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3949","checkdouble":"190285"},{"date":"11:08 03/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 La Masia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-robert-navarro-than-dong-cua-lo-la-masia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Robert Navarro c\u1ee7a Barcelona.</h2><h2>Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Navarro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Monaco \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u201cni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 16 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMonaco l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u1ecd t\u1eadp trung r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Monaco ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2 La Masia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2 La Masia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-robert-navarro-than-dong-cua-lo-la-masia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro t\u1eeb Barcelona</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Monaco \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i g\u1ea7n h\u1ebft. Kylian Mbappe c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Paris Saint-Germain. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Bernardo Silva v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy \u0111\u1ec1u gia nh\u1eadp Manchester City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a Thomas Lemar, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-liverpool-bat-ngo-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-tien-ve-fabinho-tu-monaco-172-187236.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fabinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n cho Liverpool</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Monaco \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. H\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Willem Geubbels t\u1eeb Lyon\u00a0 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Samuel Grandsir c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRobert Navarro l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stade Louis II h\u00e8 2018. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 16 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t la tinh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Navarro c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cRobertinho\u201d \u1edf l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o La Masia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Monaco:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/dai-gia-la-liga-chinh-thuc-so-huu-thomas-lemar-voi-gia-khung-180-188349.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia La Liga ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Thomas Lemar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-khung-monaco-180-187985.html\">Barca gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao kh\u1ee7ng Monaco</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3948","checkdouble":"190262"},{"date":"11:04 03/07","title":"Courtois n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 - Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00e0 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi London ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Alisson Becker v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chia tay Courtois ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 London, <strong>v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Madrid n\u1eefa</strong>&rdquo; &ndash; Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c con t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Madrid, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n ch\u00fang. B\u00ecnh t\u0129nh n\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois&nbsp;mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, v\u00e0 <strong>t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; Courtois cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, khi h\u1ecd l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n. Trong \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, khi anh ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Brazil trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois s\u1ebd c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Casemiro v\u00e0 Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid tr\u1edf n\u00ean g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lukaku d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Thong-ke-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban---Vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 2-0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3947","checkdouble":"190264"},{"date":"18:06 02/07","title":"PSG s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/18/psg-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sieu-thu-mon-vao-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Gianluigi Buffon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/chia-tay-juventus-buffon-hoi-cai-mot-chuyen-184-186551.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gianluigi Buffon x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay Juventus</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Ng\u00f4i sao 40 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/psg-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sieu-thu-mon-vao-tuan-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Buffon\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGianluigi Buffon v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao th\u00eam 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm CLB m\u1edbi ngay sau khi chia tay Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gianluigi Buffon nh\u1ea5t. Alphonse Areola l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i\u00a0s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Buffon \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Buffon s\u1ebd t\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Buffon\" title=\"thu mon Buffon\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/Gianluigi-Buffon-roi-Juventus-sau-mua-201718-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Buffon v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb L'Equipe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Buffon, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris. V\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Buffon, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Alphonse Areola ho\u1eb7c Kevin Trapp s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia ho\u1eb7c Ligue 1 quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Buffon c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Champions League thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3946","checkdouble":"190190"},{"date":"19:23 02/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2/7: M\u1edbi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, HLV Bayern \u0111\u00e3 gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-27-ngay-dau-nham-chuc-hlv-bayern-da-gieo-sau-cho-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Welbeck ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. </strong>Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tam s\u01b0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, HLV Bayern \u0111\u00e3 gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real. </strong>Niko Kovac m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Bayern Munich. Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 46 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i cho Robert Lewandowski. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern m\u00f9a sau b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o t\u1eeb Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27 HLV Bayern gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27 HLV Bayern gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-27-ngay-dau-nham-chuc-hlv-bayern-da-gieo-sau-cho-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kovac kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lewy \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern m\u00f9a sau</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Daley Blind n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU.</strong> Ajax mu\u1ed1n mua Daley Blind t\u1eeb MU. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 8 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd De Telegraaf ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho, Pogba s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U. </strong>Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Duncan Castles c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Sunday Times tin r\u1eb1ng Paul Pogba s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p gi\u1eefa ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Messi, Ronaldo. </strong>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Ronaldo hay Messi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Panama\" title=\"Hazard vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>PSG s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. </strong>Sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Gianluigi Buffon \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Juventus sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. \u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 PSG sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Rashford: \"N\u1ebfu Anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m\". </strong>Marcus Rashford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 11m khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai (3/7), Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Mexico lo s\u1ee3 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil.</strong> HLV Osorio hi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1 r\u00f5 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n \u1edf Sao Paulo tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft El Tri. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mexico \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3945","checkdouble":"190203"}]}